% As indicated, some of the transcriptions were derived from other
% sources such as Deborah Jones VIFD Music Book. The transcriptions
% were encoded in abc format (with simplifications) in order that
% I could play them as MIDI files and hear how they sound like.
%
% The abc representations  were frequently an approximation
% since it was a lot of work keying them into abc code.
% For example, all lyrics that can be found in the original were
% omitted.
%
